### Only file modified: `common/chat.cpp`

**Change 1 — New static handler function** (insert after line 1632, after `common_chat_extra_context`'s closing `}`):

```cpp
static common_chat_params common_chat_params_init_mistral_instruct_v3(
        const common_chat_template & tmpl,
        const autoparser::generation_params & inputs) {
    common_chat_params data;
    std::string prompt;
    std::string pending_system;
    bool first_user = true;

    for (const auto & msg : inputs.messages) {
        auto role    = msg.value("role", "");
        auto content = msg.value("content", "");
        if (role == "system") {
            pending_system = content;
        } else if (role == "user") {
            if (first_user) { prompt += tmpl.bos_token(); first_user = false; }
            prompt += "[INST] ";
            if (!pending_system.empty()) { prompt += pending_system + "\n"; pending_system = ""; }
            prompt += content + " [/INST]";
        } else if (role == "assistant") {
            prompt += " " + content + tmpl.eos_token();
        }
    }
    data.prompt = prompt;
    data.format = COMMON_CHAT_FORMAT_CONTENT_ONLY;
    return data;
}
```

**Change 2 — Detection block** (insert inside `common_chat_try_specialized_template()`, just before `return std::nullopt;` at line 1690):

```cpp
    if (src.find("[INST]") != std::string::npos &&
        src.find("[/INST]") != std::string::npos &&
