```

**Key decisions:**
- BOS token (`tmpl.bos_token()`) prepended only once before the first `[INST]`
- System message merged into the first user turn with `\n` separator, then cleared
- EOS token (`tmpl.eos_token()`) appended after each assistant turn  
- The `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]` absent check safely distinguishes this from the existing Ministral 3 handler (which already fires first when `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]` is present)
- No changes to `common/chat.h` — `COMMON_CHAT_FORMAT_CONTENT_ONLY` is already defined
